Subject NCSA Mosaic for X 10 available

Version 10 of NCSA Mosaic for the X Window System a networked
information systems and World Wide Web browser is hereby released

fileftpncsauiuceduMosaicxmosaicsourcexmosaic10tarZ
                            xmosaicbinariesxmosaicsunZ
